-- Bank of America, UBS Among 9 Banks Vying For Hindustan Copper Share Sale
-- Abhishek Shanker
-- 2010-06-24T10:45:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/bank-of-america-ubs-among-9-banks-vying-for-hindustan-copper-share-sale.html

          
          
             Bank of America Corp. and UBS AG are
among nine banks competing to manage a sale of Hindustan Copper
Ltd. shares by the company and the Indian government, Chairman
Shakeel Ahmed said in an interview today.  
 Kotak Mahindra Capital Co., Enam Securities Pvt., Avendus
Capital Pvt., IDBI Capital Market Services Ltd., SBI Capital
Markets Ltd., ICICI Securities Ltd. and IDFC-SSKI Ltd. also
submitted their bids, Ahmed said.  
